name: axios
text: The national lockdown is easing and the pandemic is no longer the single dominant storyline of our lives, but nothing has really changed — we didn’t develop a treatment and the virus didn’t get naturally weaker. It’s just as contagious as it ever was. https://t.co/0SruEO33Lg

name: axios
text:
What we've learned:
•  This coronavirus doesn’t survive on surfaces as long as once feared
• It appears to transmit much more easily indoors than outside
• It is deadliest for people older than 60 or who have an underlying medical condition https://t.co/0SruEO33Lg
